1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:01,980
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><font color="#171209">Might Tower</font></b></font>

2
00:00:01,360 --> 00:00:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, we continue with an overview of All 
Might's direction in the next season...</font>

3
00:00:01,980 --> 00:00:02,980
<font size="20"><b>{\an1}<font color="#513c3b"><font size="8">P{*\3c&HA3A2E2&}l{*\3c&HA3A3E2&}a{*\3c&HA4A4E3&}n{*\3c&HA5A5E3&}n{*\3c&HA5A6E3&}i{*\3c&HA6A7E3&}n{*\3c&HA7A8E4&}g {*\3c&HA8A9E4&}A{*\3c&HA9AAE4&}l{*\3c&HA9ABE4&}l {*\3c&HAAADE5&}M{*\3c&HABAEE5&}i{*\3c&HACAFE5&}g{*\3c&HACB0E6&}h{*\3c&HADB1E6&}t{*\3c&HAEB2E6&}'{*\3c&HAEB3E6&}s {*\3c&HB0B5E7&}D{*\3c&HB0B6E7&}i{*\3c&HB1B7E7&}r{*\3c&HB2B8E7&}e{*\3c&HB2B8E8&}c{*\3c&HB3B9E8&}t{*\3c&HB4BAE8&}i{*\3c&HB4BBE8&}o{*\3c&HB5BCE9&}n {*\3c&HB6BEE9&}f{*\3c&HB7BFE9&}o{*\3c&HB8C0E9&}r {*\3c&HB9C2EA&}t{*\3c&HBAC3EA&}h{*\3c&HBAC4EA&}e {*\3c&HBBC6EB&}N{*\3c&HBCC7EB&}e{*\3c&HBDC7EB&}x{*\3c&HBDC8EB&}t {*\3c&HBFCAEC&}S{*\3c&HBFCBEC&}e{*\3c&HC0CCEC&}a{*\3c&HC1CDED&}s{*\3c&HC1CEED&}on</font></font></b></font>

4
00:00:06,140 --> 00:00:09,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you'd all open up the 
document in the shared folder.</font>

5
00:00:09,670 --> 00:00:10,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Currently...</font>

6
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:13,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Yagi?</font>

7
00:00:13,660 --> 00:00:16,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please put your phone on 
silent during meetings.</font>

8
00:00:16,840 --> 00:00:18,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">E-Excuse me.</font>

9
00:00:18,990 --> 00:00:20,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I need to run to the bathroom.</font>

10
00:00:20,710 --> 00:00:21,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mr. Yagi?</font>

11
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:26,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Tsukauchi? You 
normally just message—</font>

12
00:00:26,130 --> 00:00:29,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might! There's an emergency 
at the Tokyo Sky Egg!</font>

13
00:00:30,210 --> 00:00:31,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsukauchi?</font>

14
00:00:40,890 --> 00:00:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Sky Egg...</font>

15
00:00:42,670 --> 00:00:43,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is falling!</font>

16
00:00:58,130 --> 00:01:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There we go. The catastrophe 
is already a done deal.</font>

17
00:01:03,360 --> 00:01:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't fight fate, y'know?</font>

18
00:01:06,560 --> 00:01:09,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not unless you're a god or something.</font>

19
00:02:40,340 --> 00:02:47,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an1}<font size="40"><font color="#c5000e">deus ex machina</font></font></b></font>

20
00:02:42,260 --> 00:02:47,390
<font face="Times New Roman" size="20"><b>{\an7}A type of storytelling device codified in Ancient Greek theater. "The god from the machine."  Typically
 identified by a forced conclusion to a series
of events; a narrative contrivance.</b></font>

21
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:48,390
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b><i>{\an1}<font size="30"><font color="#ffe640">This Is a Hero!!</font></font></i></b></font>

22
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:55,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makoto!</font>

23
00:02:55,850 --> 00:02:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tsukauchi, what was that noise?</font>

24
00:02:58,230 --> 00:03:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mentioned the Sky Egg?</font>

25
00:03:03,330 --> 00:03:04,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nao!</font>

26
00:03:06,070 --> 00:03:07,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home!</font>

27
00:03:09,130 --> 00:03:11,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you come straight home?</font>

28
00:03:11,780 --> 00:03:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

29
00:03:13,600 --> 00:03:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're telling the truth!</font>

30
00:03:15,530 --> 00:03:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I went to the hospital with Mom.</font>

31
00:03:19,450 --> 00:03:22,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you worried about me?</font>

32
00:03:25,690 --> 00:03:27,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, not really.</font>

33
00:03:27,630 --> 00:03:29,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lying!</font>

34
00:03:30,170 --> 00:03:32,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mom, what did the tests show?</font>

35
00:03:32,770 --> 00:03:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's something like a mind-reading Quirk.</font>

36
00:03:37,390 --> 00:03:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I figured...</font>

37
00:03:39,920 --> 00:03:42,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always knew she was 
a sharp girl, but...</font>

38
00:03:48,750 --> 00:03:54,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love you, Nao! Do you love me?</font>

39
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:58,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mako, you shouldn't ask 
people questions like that.</font>

40
00:03:58,880 --> 00:04:01,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, it's fine. Adorable, even.</font>

41
00:04:01,830 --> 00:04:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want her making a habit of it!</font>

42
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Constantly probing people's 
emotions isn't good for anyone!</font>

43
00:04:07,320 --> 00:04:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're so serious, Nao.</font>

44
00:04:12,540 --> 00:04:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Answer me this time! 
Do you love me, Nao?</font>

45
00:04:16,940 --> 00:04:17,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like I said...</font>

46
00:04:18,730 --> 00:04:22,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you're going to keep forcing 
the issue... then no.</font>

47
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,700
<font size="20"><b>{\an8}<font size="30"><font color="#ffffff">Mr. Yagi</font></font></b></font>

48
00:04:23,960 --> 00:04:28,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As a police officer, it's inappropriate 
to make this kind of request.</font>

49
00:04:29,350 --> 00:04:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm doing it anyway!</font>

50
00:04:33,130 --> 00:04:34,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you hate me?</font>

51
00:04:39,350 --> 00:04:41,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're lying!</font>

52
00:04:43,370 --> 00:04:45,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-Please save her...</font>

53
00:04:50,210 --> 00:04:54,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, save my little sister, All Might!</font>

54
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right.</font>

55
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:01,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand, and I'll be right there.</font>

56
00:05:01,750 --> 00:05:03,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yet I don't dare say it.</font>

57
00:05:05,320 --> 00:05:08,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The reason being...</font>

58
00:05:08,140 --> 00:05:14,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's only one thing I should 
say at a time like this.</font>

59
00:05:16,380 --> 00:05:18,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As to what those words are—</font>

60
00:05:19,140 --> 00:05:19,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that...</font>

61
00:05:19,950 --> 00:05:21,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might!</font>

62
00:05:21,710 --> 00:05:24,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I am here!"</font>

63
00:05:29,050 --> 00:05:32,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Smash!</font>

64
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might!</font>

65
00:05:57,000 --> 00:05:58,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might did it all on his own!</font>

66
00:05:58,870 --> 00:06:01,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The dude just set the Sky Egg down!</font>

67
00:06:01,090 --> 00:06:01,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow!</font>

68
00:06:01,840 --> 00:06:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy crap!</font>

69
00:06:05,340 --> 00:06:10,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might! All Might! All Might!</font>

70
00:06:10,180 --> 00:06:15,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might! All Might! 
All Might! All Might!</font>

71
00:06:13,630 --> 00:06:15,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Are we saved?</font>

72
00:06:19,980 --> 00:06:21,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might!</font>

73
00:06:22,220 --> 00:06:23,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That chanting...</font>

74
00:06:24,190 --> 00:06:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might?</font>

75
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:28,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That must be it! All Might saved us!</font>

76
00:06:28,900 --> 00:06:31,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-Thank goodness...</font>

77
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:42,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The number one hero always 
makes the impossible possible.</font>

78
00:06:47,650 --> 00:06:49,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's All Might?</font>

79
00:06:50,220 --> 00:06:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Japan's number one hero...</font>

80
00:06:53,300 --> 00:06:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might! Quick, over here!</font>

81
00:07:01,640 --> 00:07:05,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey there. It's a pleasure, 
Captain Celebrity.</font>

82
00:07:05,190 --> 00:07:06,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you.</font>

83
00:07:06,970 --> 00:07:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Congratulations on a job well done.</font>

84
00:07:09,490 --> 00:07:10,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you are?</font>

85
00:07:11,200 --> 00:07:12,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a fan!</font>

86
00:07:12,750 --> 00:07:14,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I get an autograph?</font>

87
00:07:14,550 --> 00:07:15,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd be a pleasure.</font>

88
00:07:17,270 --> 00:07:19,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might, can we get a comment?</font>

89
00:07:20,610 --> 00:07:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm mostly glad this wrapped 
up with no fatalities.</font>

90
00:07:23,130 --> 00:07:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That said, we have plenty of 
injured and anxious people here.</font>

91
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:29,760
<font size="20"><b><font color="#4b161c">{\an1}All Might Resolves Sky Egg Attack In An Instant!!</font></b></font>

92
00:07:28,300 --> 00:07:33,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To that end, public 
services and pro heroes</font>

93
00:07:33,150 --> 00:07:37,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">will be working together to wrap things up 
in the best way possible.</font>

94
00:07:37,010 --> 00:07:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my hope that you'll all 
support all of these heroes!</font>

95
00:07:41,840 --> 00:07:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the hell?</font>

96
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's safe now! Please 
evacuate without rushing!</font>

97
00:07:48,150 --> 00:07:51,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief. I guess I don't get 
to be the hero this time.</font>

98
00:07:52,360 --> 00:07:55,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be ridiculous, Captain!</font>

99
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:58,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And check it out! All Might 
autographed this for me!</font>

100
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:01,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't help but notice a difference</font>

101
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}So awesome! Oh, man, I can't 
ever wash this now!</font>

102
00:08:01,240 --> 00:08:03,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in your reaction to when 
I gave you my autograph.</font>

103
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:07,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anyone is thirsty, 
we have tea to drink!</font>

104
00:08:07,680 --> 00:08:10,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We have C.C. dumplings, too!</font>

105
00:08:10,610 --> 00:08:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's your tea.</font>

106
00:08:11,930 --> 00:08:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And that's your sister?</font>

107
00:08:12,540 --> 00:08:13,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There you go.</font>

108
00:08:14,040 --> 00:08:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad she's all right.</font>

109
00:08:16,150 --> 00:08:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">About that... I'm sorry 
for losing my composure.</font>

110
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, none of that, please!</font>

111
00:08:21,700 --> 00:08:27,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If anything, you being so upset 
is part of how I made it in time.</font>

112
00:08:28,040 --> 00:08:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that how it works?</font>

113
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be surprised what a big difference</font>

114
00:08:32,050 --> 00:08:34,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">your state of mind makes in terms 
of what you can accomplish.</font>

115
00:08:35,250 --> 00:08:39,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You made a point of separating 
public and private before,</font>

116
00:08:39,620 --> 00:08:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I think that personally listening to
cries for help is part of a hero's job.</font>

117
00:08:47,440 --> 00:08:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the whole reason I received this 
power is to give hope to people.</font>

118
00:08:53,420 --> 00:08:56,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hope that their voices can 
reach the number one hero.</font>

119
00:08:57,580 --> 00:08:59,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Received... your power?</font>

120
00:08:59,630 --> 00:09:01,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nothing.</font>

121
00:09:01,570 --> 00:09:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All right, Tsukauchi, shall 
we help with the recovery?</font>

122
00:09:06,300 --> 00:09:07,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Right.</font>

123
00:09:07,730 --> 00:09:10,690
<font face="Verdana" size="20"><b>{\an8}<font color="#a23c51"><font size="25">NaruFest!</font></font></b></font>

124
00:09:09,520 --> 00:09:15,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One day, I'll tell you everything. 
All of All Might's secrets.</font>

125
00:09:18,510 --> 00:09:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this? What the hell?</font>

126
00:09:20,620 --> 00:09:24,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is everybody acting 
like that's a wrap?</font>

127
00:09:26,620 --> 00:09:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do they even realize I've been 
holding back this whole time?!</font>

128
00:09:29,880 --> 00:09:32,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They better not think 
they've won, dammit.</font>

129
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure they all die 
out of spite if I have to.</font>

130
00:09:39,200 --> 00:09:42,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Regenerate and fuse together all the 
pieces of the suicide bomber villain...</font>

131
00:09:42,570 --> 00:09:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have them increase in size, and then...</font>

132
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:54,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?!</font>

133
00:09:54,900 --> 00:09:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

134
00:09:56,030 --> 00:09:57,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's monster-sized!</font>

135
00:09:57,490 --> 00:09:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A colossal bomb villain?!</font>

136
00:10:00,710 --> 00:10:03,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just big, either.</font>

137
00:10:03,410 --> 00:10:08,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something of that size would be 
easy for Eraser Head to shut down,</font>

138
00:10:08,560 --> 00:10:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or All Might to send flying.</font>

139
00:10:12,640 --> 00:10:15,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this bad boy's custom made.</font>

140
00:10:15,990 --> 00:10:19,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I call it the cluster bomber.</font>

141
00:10:19,010 --> 00:10:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can release 200 of the bombs it's 
generated in its guts all at once!</font>

142
00:10:23,580 --> 00:10:26,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might can't handle that number alone,</font>

143
00:10:26,210 --> 00:10:30,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and even if every hero here teamed up, 
they'd maybe be able to stop half of them!</font>

144
00:10:31,040 --> 00:10:34,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The other half... the 
remaining hundred...</font>

145
00:10:34,030 --> 00:10:36,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The audience that thought they were safe,</font>

146
00:10:36,210 --> 00:10:38,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the emergency responders who showed 
up to help, and while they're at it,</font>

147
00:10:38,600 --> 00:10:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">all of the folks in the area who 
are just living their lives...</font>

148
00:10:41,890 --> 00:10:44,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">are gonna be blown sky high!</font>

149
00:10:51,260 --> 00:10:53,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A swarm of those exploding villains?!</font>

150
00:10:53,010 --> 00:10:54,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's way too many!</font>

151
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no!</font>

152
00:11:05,220 --> 00:11:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nebraska Smash!</font>

153
00:11:16,220 --> 00:11:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One punch?!</font>

154
00:11:18,960 --> 00:11:21,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He caught all of the bombs in
the vortex created by a single punch</font>

155
00:11:21,990 --> 00:11:24,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and they're detonating 
safely inside of it?</font>

156
00:11:29,460 --> 00:11:33,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's awesome! And insane!</font>

157
00:11:33,130 --> 00:11:36,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't believe there's anyone in the 
world who can pull off an OP move like that!</font>

158
00:11:37,380 --> 00:11:40,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Indeed there is, Number 6.</i></font>

159
00:11:40,410 --> 00:11:46,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As hard as it might be to believe, 
what you're seeing is reality.</i></font>

160
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He does in fact exist.</i></font>

161
00:11:49,230 --> 00:11:53,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This man who defies the standards 
that all other heroes live by...</i></font>

162
00:11:53,140 --> 00:11:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A genuine superhuman.</i></font>

163
00:11:56,660 --> 00:12:01,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A veritable deus ex machina, capable of 
bending physics and fate to his will.</i></font>

164
00:12:01,580 --> 00:12:04,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's who All Might is.</i></font>

165
00:12:04,160 --> 00:12:07,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The symbol of the heights 
you seek to reach.</i></font>

166
00:12:07,540 --> 00:12:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That I seek to reach, huh?</font>

167
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I never said anything about 
wanting to be All Might, y'know.</font>

168
00:12:16,710 --> 00:12:18,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I suppose that's true.</i></font>

169
00:12:18,580 --> 00:12:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And I prefer that you're free 
to act as you see fit.</i></font>

170
00:12:23,270 --> 00:12:23,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks—</font>

171
00:12:28,380 --> 00:12:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Factory's objective was creating 
composite Quirks via human experimentation</font>

172
00:12:33,590 --> 00:12:35,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and application of drugs.</font>

173
00:12:36,180 --> 00:12:38,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was easy to predict he'd use an event</font>

174
00:12:38,100 --> 00:12:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">featuring all-star heroes 
to run an experiment.</font>

175
00:12:41,410 --> 00:12:47,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I had already confirmed which building 
was best for monitoring the Sky Egg.</font>

176
00:12:47,870 --> 00:12:50,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A distance of 250 meters,</font>

177
00:12:50,070 --> 00:12:53,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">with a wind speed of eight meters 
per second from the southwest.</font>

178
00:12:54,080 --> 00:12:55,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Aiming for the head.</i></font>

179
00:13:04,050 --> 00:13:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something flew by my 
line of fire. A bird?</i></font>

180
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:09,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I missed my mark.</i></font>

181
00:13:09,520 --> 00:13:10,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But he shouldn't be able to move.</i></font>

182
00:13:21,980 --> 00:13:24,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, hello there.</font>

183
00:13:24,870 --> 00:13:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're a fast one.</font>

184
00:13:26,820 --> 00:13:31,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I guess you've tinkered with your body, 
on top of that acceleration Quirk.</font>

185
00:13:31,730 --> 00:13:34,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A fair bit, yeah.</font>

186
00:13:34,100 --> 00:13:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lately I've been trying 
to boost my muscle mass</font>

187
00:13:35,950 --> 00:13:39,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and tuning down my pain receptors, 
trying to get the right touches.</font>

188
00:13:39,000 --> 00:13:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As far as the acceleration... or to 
be more specific, my Overclocking.</font>

189
00:13:42,920 --> 00:13:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I got that one from a certain 
high-speed hero—O'Clock.</font>

190
00:13:47,210 --> 00:13:50,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't know how long I've 
waited to meet you, Master.</font>

191
00:13:50,490 --> 00:13:53,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been looking all over for you, too.</font>

192
00:13:53,700 --> 00:13:55,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who the hell are you, anyway?</font>

193
00:13:56,830 --> 00:13:59,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The scarred man behind 
the modified villains.</font>

194
00:13:59,740 --> 00:14:02,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No ID, no record,
and not so much as a name.</font>

195
00:14:02,910 --> 00:14:09,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All anyone knows about you is that you 
have my stolen Quirk—Overclock.</font>

196
00:14:10,210 --> 00:14:14,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means I've got a ton of questions, 
but let's start with a name.</font>

197
00:14:14,850 --> 00:14:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A name? You want my name?</font>

198
00:14:18,120 --> 00:14:21,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And, like, you're actually interested 
in me? Aw, it's an honor.</font>

199
00:14:21,880 --> 00:14:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The sad truth is, I'm literally nobody.</font>

200
00:14:26,190 --> 00:14:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Early on, I was literally just a tiny, 
little, poorly-defined critter.</font>

201
00:14:30,200 --> 00:14:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Experiment Subject 6. Most people 
referred to me as Number 6.</font>

202
00:14:34,920 --> 00:14:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that's just a number, not a name.</font>

203
00:14:38,520 --> 00:14:42,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm going to become somebody... 
somebody important...</font>

204
00:14:43,400 --> 00:14:44,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O'Clock.</font>

205
00:14:45,170 --> 00:14:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the only name I wanna go by!</font>

206
00:14:49,830 --> 00:14:54,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Funny. Most kids with big dreams 
about becoming somebody...</font>

207
00:14:54,060 --> 00:14:58,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">tend to want to be All Might.</font>

208
00:14:58,740 --> 00:15:00,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might, huh?</font>

209
00:15:00,930 --> 00:15:05,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, he is impressive. But being 
him seems like such a drag...</font>

210
00:15:05,790 --> 00:15:09,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, whether it's fighting 
villains or disaster recovery,</font>

211
00:15:09,460 --> 00:15:13,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">he's constantly cleaning 
up other people's messes.</font>

212
00:15:14,630 --> 00:15:17,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what makes him 
the number one hero.</font>

213
00:15:17,460 --> 00:15:22,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All of humanity is lucky 
that he's so selfless.</font>

214
00:15:23,470 --> 00:15:27,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If someone with that kind of power 
used it for selfish purposes...</font>

215
00:15:27,290 --> 00:15:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">it'd mean the end of the world.</font>

216
00:15:30,760 --> 00:15:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's just what I'm talking about!</font>

217
00:15:32,520 --> 00:15:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All Might is too strong for his own good!</font>

218
00:15:36,490 --> 00:15:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Save the world, or destroy it.</font>

219
00:15:40,800 --> 00:15:42,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's got two options.</font>

220
00:15:42,550 --> 00:15:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can't use his power freely. 
And that doesn't work for me.</font>

221
00:15:47,200 --> 00:15:51,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm trying to go my own 
way, and live free.</font>

222
00:15:51,760 --> 00:15:54,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're not interested 
in helping others?</font>

223
00:15:54,390 --> 00:15:59,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wouldn't rule it out completely, 
but I can't deny it doesn't suit me.</font>

224
00:15:59,820 --> 00:16:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which is why I wanna be you, Master!</font>

225
00:16:03,620 --> 00:16:07,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't need the kinda power 
to send a building flying.</font>

226
00:16:07,080 --> 00:16:10,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Quirk that gives me the initiative, 
no matter who I'm facing...</font>

227
00:16:10,870 --> 00:16:14,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can force the first move and win before
the other guy knows what happened!</font>

228
00:16:15,100 --> 00:16:20,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's O'Clock! My hero! 
It gives me the chills!</font>

229
00:16:20,660 --> 00:16:24,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's nothing heroic 
about someone like that.</font>

230
00:16:24,100 --> 00:16:26,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be so modest, big man.</font>

231
00:16:27,970 --> 00:16:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm already a mega fan of yours.</font>

232
00:16:30,360 --> 00:16:34,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know everything there is to know about 
you, and will do anything to become you.</font>

233
00:16:34,980 --> 00:16:38,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I saw your last 
act, it gave me chills!</font>

234
00:16:40,740 --> 00:16:42,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I knew that I was next.</font>

235
00:16:43,300 --> 00:16:46,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was gonna be my turn, now.</font>

236
00:16:47,570 --> 00:16:50,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I've got a bit of a request to make.</font>

237
00:16:50,020 --> 00:16:53,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like you to publicly 
accept me as your heir.</font>

238
00:16:53,230 --> 00:16:57,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I'm gonna do this, I'd like to be the 
official second generation O'Clock.</font>

239
00:17:01,590 --> 00:17:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, kid, but I've already 
got an apprentice.</font>

240
00:17:06,770 --> 00:17:09,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, right, you mean Koichi?</font>

241
00:17:09,940 --> 00:17:15,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotta say, it's pretty clear 
I respect you more than him.</font>

242
00:17:15,350 --> 00:17:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, he's a fan of 
All Might's, not you.</font>

243
00:17:19,540 --> 00:17:21,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's exactly it.</font>

244
00:17:21,930 --> 00:17:25,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I already told you—O'Clock 
wasn't a hero.</font>

245
00:17:25,400 --> 00:17:30,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And if someone who wants to be him 
has managed to obtain his Quirk...</font>

246
00:17:31,310 --> 00:17:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They'd be a terrible villain.</font>

247
00:17:34,260 --> 00:17:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The kind of threat to society 
that needs to be taken down.</font>

248
00:17:37,290 --> 00:17:40,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that's how it's gonna be? 
Labeling me a villain?</font>

249
00:17:40,890 --> 00:17:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, I can work with that.</font>

250
00:17:43,450 --> 00:17:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So, what are you gonna do then? 
Shoot me with that rifle?</font>

251
00:17:48,090 --> 00:17:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You already botched your sniping attempt.</font>

252
00:17:50,620 --> 00:17:54,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or are you thinking you 
can't miss at this range?</font>

253
00:17:55,420 --> 00:17:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just try it!</font>

254
00:17:58,910 --> 00:18:00,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">See? Missed again.</font>

255
00:18:00,930 --> 00:18:05,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really did respect you, Mr. 
Formerly-Known-As-O'Clock.</font>

256
00:18:05,640 --> 00:18:08,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you're just some 
guy without your Quirk.</font>

257
00:18:08,730 --> 00:18:11,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And once I'm sped up, you can't stop me.</font>

258
00:18:11,770 --> 00:18:17,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye, Master. Once you're 
gone, I'll be O'Clock!</font>

259
00:18:17,650 --> 00:18:21,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Can you hear this message, Overclock?</i></font>

260
00:18:21,550 --> 00:18:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is that?</font>

261
00:18:23,040 --> 00:18:25,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A recorded message...</font>

262
00:18:24,670 --> 00:18:29,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Even if you have have obtained 
O'Clock's high-speed Quirk,</font>

263
00:18:25,280 --> 00:18:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Played back at high speed?</font>

264
00:18:29,730 --> 00:18:34,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I doubt that means you fully 
comprehend its nature just yet.</i></font>

265
00:18:34,770 --> 00:18:39,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The true nature of the Quirk, Overclock, 
is a catalyzation of the brain's functions.</i></font>

266
00:18:39,180 --> 00:18:44,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Your perception and cognition go
faster, creating a slow-motion sensation.</i></font>

267
00:18:44,230 --> 00:18:48,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That acceleration rate isn't uniform.
It varies depending on mental state.</i></font>

268
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:51,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When aiming to deliver a physical attack, 
it tends to reach anywhere from two,</i></font>

269
00:18:51,710 --> 00:18:53,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>three times, to ten times acceleration.</i></font>

270
00:18:53,990 --> 00:18:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When responding to a sudden threat, you 
get several dozen times a reaction speed.</i></font>

271
00:18:58,460 --> 00:19:00,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>With enough focus, it can be increased</i></font>

272
00:19:00,630 --> 00:19:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>to the point that the world around 
you literally seems frozen.</i></font>

273
00:19:05,000 --> 00:19:08,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But that kind of high level acceleration 
comes with time limits.</i></font>

274
00:19:08,760 --> 00:19:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Think of it as your brain running out 
of breath during intense exercise.</i></font>

275
00:19:12,710 --> 00:19:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The faster the brain has accelerated, 
the faster it wears the brain out.</i></font>

276
00:19:17,450 --> 00:19:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For example, when dodging 
a bullet from a rifle...</i></font>

277
00:19:21,300 --> 00:19:26,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or maybe when trying to perceive a 
message played back at 300x speed.</i></font>

278
00:19:28,810 --> 00:19:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My Quirk!</font>

279
00:19:30,300 --> 00:19:32,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like you're out of breath!</font>

280
00:19:32,990 --> 00:19:36,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, but I'm not giving 
you a chance to recover!</font>

281
00:19:38,580 --> 00:19:40,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explosions!</font>

282
00:19:40,640 --> 00:19:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't maneuver how I want in the air!</font>

283
00:19:43,210 --> 00:19:45,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just blew up the top three floors!</font>

284
00:19:45,850 --> 00:19:48,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This kind of free fall will 
keep you from speeding up.</font>

285
00:19:48,300 --> 00:19:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A shotgun!</font>

286
00:19:49,880 --> 00:19:53,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd protect your head. It's 
one of your most vital parts.</font>

287
00:19:53,880 --> 00:19:56,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although you'd need your 
legs to land safely.</font>

288
00:19:58,130 --> 00:20:00,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You said you'd tweaked your 
pain sensitivity, right?</font>

289
00:20:00,980 --> 00:20:04,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I need to physically 
stop your limbs from working.</font>

290
00:20:13,820 --> 00:20:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, this is weird.</font>

291
00:20:15,990 --> 00:20:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were aiming for a headshot before, 
and now wanna take me alive?</font>

292
00:20:20,390 --> 00:20:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you even know what you wanna do?</font>

293
00:20:22,490 --> 00:20:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a matter of efficacy.</font>

294
00:20:25,220 --> 00:20:29,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A lethal approach was ideal when 
targeting you from a distance.</font>

295
00:20:29,550 --> 00:20:34,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if your target's trapped in a 
cage? Then you can take them alive.</font>

296
00:20:34,870 --> 00:20:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally, the next detonation 
will drop the entire building.</font>

297
00:20:39,420 --> 00:20:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if you accelerate, you 
won't be able to escape.</font>

298
00:20:42,940 --> 00:20:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The cage will become a 
coffin at that point.</font>

299
00:20:45,950 --> 00:20:47,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is checkmate for you.</font>

300
00:20:47,820 --> 00:20:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you want me to accept defeat?</font>

301
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:53,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cuz you don't wanna kill 
me if you don't have to?</font>

302
00:20:53,140 --> 00:20:56,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">While you've been explaining 
what a big softy you are,</font>

303
00:20:56,670 --> 00:20:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've managed to recover enough to—</font>

304
00:21:00,190 --> 00:21:03,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eliminating a dangerous 
villain is my top priority,</font>

305
00:21:03,810 --> 00:21:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but the chance to learn more about 
the mastermind is tempting.</font>

306
00:21:06,780 --> 00:21:10,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incidentally! Another way! 
To shut down Overclock!</font>

307
00:21:10,660 --> 00:21:13,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is a concussion! Via blunt force trauma!</font>

308
00:21:13,480 --> 00:21:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In other words! As long as I'm 
hitting you! You can't speed up!</font>

309
00:21:18,060 --> 00:21:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once I've beaten you, I'll restrain you,
and we'll have a little interview.</font>

310
00:21:24,450 --> 00:21:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you regenerate faster, too?</font>

311
00:21:27,100 --> 00:21:29,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The bleeding from where I 
sniped you has stopped.</font>

312
00:21:30,230 --> 00:21:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Pretty dangerous, but not much 
he can do once he's tied up.</font>

313
00:21:35,640 --> 00:21:38,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bad call, Master.</font>

314
00:21:38,010 --> 00:21:42,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You should've gone blown my head 
off when you had the chance.</font>

315
00:21:42,430 --> 00:21:46,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">By parasitizing my body with 
the bomber villain's cells,</font>

316
00:21:46,080 --> 00:21:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can turn my arms into explosives!</font>

317
00:23:25,770 --> 00:23:30,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The string of events drew to a close,
and the Captain returned to America.</font>

318
00:23:30,010 --> 00:23:33,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two years have passed. And 
I've made a certain decision.</font>

319
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,260
<font size="20"><b><font color="#353b39"><font size="25">Storage Room</font></font></b></font>

320
00:23:31,720 --> 00:23:33,260
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="20"><b><font color="#222d25"><font size="33">Interview Room</font></font></b></font>

321
00:23:33,570 --> 00:23:35,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next time: Graduation and Career Path.</font>

322
00:23:35,960 --> 00:23:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Koichi Haimawari is graduating 
from being the Crawler!</font>

323
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:40,050
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b><font color="#ec3778"><font size="13">Limited Time Only!!</font></font></b></font>

324
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:40,050
<font face="Arial Black" size="20"><b><font color="#ec3778"><font size="13">Limited Time Only!!</font></font></b></font>

